{"tid":86749,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸一女子玩VR跳樓遊戲出意外 ,臉重重著地跌斷門牙","createTime":"2017-01-19T09:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T12:37:48.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9266f0b2d393bd9b0958fcb63a4cef64e6e4bacf","tid":86749,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:54:54.000Z","msg":"著VR虛擬現實技術的不斷普及，各種體驗、遊戲活動吸引了越來越多的人參與，但是這當中卻隱藏著一些不安全因素。近日，昆明的陸女士就因此受傷了。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tv.cctv.com/2017/01/18/VIDEeSGu5wfgIVmU0cMykYva170118.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftv.cctv.com%2F2017%2F01%2F18%2FVIDEeSGu5wfgIVmU0cMykYva170118.shtml&d=ziwUO1pVl6ACsftRMy3zUoscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=961720a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tv.cctv.com/2017/01/18/VIDEeSGu5wfgIVmU0cMykYva170118.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n陸女士說，當天她和家人到商場時，看到有一個VR體驗區，交了15元後，獲得了一次玩遊戲的機會。隨後，工作人員推薦她玩一次跳樓遊戲。從事發時的閉路電視畫面可以看到，當時現場有20人左右，陸女士先是腳步跳起來了一下，隨後整個身體就摔倒在了地面上。當時有幾名工作人員在旁邊，但沒有人注意陳女士的動作，直到陳女士摔倒在地上以後，幾名工作人員趕緊上前。事故導致陸女士面部受傷，兩顆門牙斷裂。事後，經過陸女士與活動主辦方多次協商，最終陸女士獲賠3萬元。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://wx3.sinaimg.cn/mw690/6236c2bcly1fbutow1carg20hh094e81.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwx3.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F6236c2bcly1fbutow1carg20hh094e81.gif&h=8b2b1a23&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n律師建議，遇到此類情況，要及時收集相關的證據，比如閉路電視片段、圍觀的群眾。同時，要及時去檢查、資料，保留醫院單據、收據憑證。如果無法協商，可以通過訴訟程序來解決糾紛。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2017/01/20170118_ll_136_2/gamersky_01origin_01_201711815422A2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2017%2F01%2F20170118_ll_136_2%2Fgamersky_01origin_01_201711815422A2.jpg&h=013335bf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n專業人士介紹，VR遊戲中，一些運動類、體感類的遊戲，在快速移動過程中會造成一種體感差，使玩家感覺身體失重，造成錯覺，導致跌倒。因此盡量坐著玩，如果站著的話，要有人在旁邊進行攙扶，做好保護工作。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170118/s00004/1484735594424SL4_D6E3DF8549E29FC54811EA95E30667FE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170118%2Fs00004%2F1484735594424SL4_D6E3DF8549E29FC54811EA95E30667FE.jpg&h=201ad061&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170118/s00004/1484728416305SL4_BE803D2AD983E530192E0AF02DBE240E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170118%2Fs00004%2F1484728416305SL4_BE803D2AD983E530192E0AF02DBE240E.jpg&h=5b1506e4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170118/s00004/1484728415619SL4_9185FE258AC4FACCC032368D285AC189.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170118%2Fs00004%2F1484728415619SL4_9185FE258AC4FACCC032368D285AC189.jpg&h=7c1430ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9afaed655124d712155469d704853bd83bb457e3","tid":86749,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:56:39.000Z","msg":"15文賠3萬文<br />\n支那專才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3823e5d68c6d011a58e2faeb1805035addbafcac","tid":86749,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:57:00.000Z","msg":"竟然拎到三萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9b78eedd36ae980ed1ed426e0fd862bfda891b","tid":86749,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:58:07.000Z","msg":"弱鳩智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe2a033d49f5cebd397faa3dc43c755a6e82d79","tid":86749,"uid":32325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T11:13:57.000Z","msg":"低鳩能<img src=\"/assets/faces/no